Package: ndotr
Title: NDOT Rain on Snow Decision Support
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Brennan", "Bean", , "brennan.bean@usu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides the data and functions necessary to implement
    the Heggli et al. (2023) Rain on Snow (ROS) Terrestrial Water Input (TWI) 
    decision support tool as presented to the Nevada Department of 
    Transportation (NDOT). 
